    SELECT [e].[EMPLOYEE_ID], [e].[BIRTH_DATE], [e].[CREATED_AT], [e].[CREATED_BY], [e].[DEPARTMENT_ID], [e].[EMAIL], [e].[EMPLOYEE_NUMBER], [e].[FIRST_NAME_AR], [e].[FULL_NAME_EN], [e].[GENDER], [e].[HIRE_DATE], [e].[IS_ACTIVE], [e].[IS_DELETED], [e].[JOB_ID], [e].[LAST_NAME_AR], [e].[LICENSE_EXPIRY_DATE], [e].[LICENSE_NUMBER], [e].[MANAGER_ID], [e].[MARITAL_STATUS], [e].[MOBILE], [e].[NATIONAL_ID], [e].[NATIONALITY_ID], [e].[PROFILE_PICTURE_PATH], [e].[SECOND_NAME_AR], [e].[SPECIALTY], [e].[TERMINATION_DATE], [e].[THIRD_NAME_AR], [e].[UPDATED_AT], [e].[UPDATED_BY], [e].[USER_ID], [e].[VERSION_NO]

    WHERE [e].[IS_DELETED] = CAST(0 AS tinyint)
    ORDER BY [e].[CREATED_AT] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [e0]
INNER JOIN [HR_CORE].[DEPARTMENTS] AS [d] ON [e0].[DEPARTMENT_ID] = [d].[DEPT_ID]
INNER JOIN [HR_CORE].[JOBS] AS [j] ON [e0].[JOB_ID] = [j].[JOB_ID]
ORDER BY [e0].[CREATED_AT] DESC
